==应用==
聚四氢呋喃主要用于弹性纤维的合成，如[[氨纶|氨纶]]<ref name="kirk"/>和聚氨酯。后者的工艺中聚氨酯作为前聚体之一首先溶于溶剂。<ref>Ashford's Dictionary of Industrial Chemicals, third edition, 2011, page 7587</ref>用于人造革的制造时，聚四氢呋喃与[[异氰酸酯|异氰酸酯]]同为原料，或与异氰酸其他衍生物反应，得到聚氨酯。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://terathane.invista.com/e-trolley/page_10324/index.html|title=Uses of PTMEG polyols|accessdate=2007-09-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070827021423/http://terathane.invista.com/e-trolley/page_10324/index.html|archivedate=2007-08-27}}</ref> 

==合成==
聚四氢呋喃主要通过四氢呋喃的聚合反应制造。<ref name="kirk">{{cite encyclopedia |year=1996 |title =Polyethers, Tetrahydrofuran and Oxetane Polymers |first1=Gerfried |last1=Pruckmayr |first2= P. |last2=Dreyfuss |first3= M. P. |last3=Dreyfuss |encyclopedia=Kirk‑Othmer Encyclopedia of Chemical Technology |publisher=John Wiley & Sons, Inc |location= |id= }}</ref>整个过程从天然气开始，合成甲醛，然后得丁二醛，丁二醇，催化脱水得四氢呋喃，最后开环聚合。

